pavithra ( 1994 ) ( tamil : &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ) is a tamil film written , produced and directed by k. subash under his home banner , &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; films . the film features raadhika in the lead role with nassar and ajith kumar in supporting roles . the film 's music was by a. r. rahman and lyrics by vairamuthu . the film opened on november 2 , 1994 as one among the deepavali releases and received critical acclaim .